  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Three education projects have been merged to make one education project titled: &#x2018;ACE&#x2019;- Access of Children with Disabilities to Education as of 2013. The project goal is to strengthen systems to increase access to education for children with disabilities. 
Specific Objectives are: 
Objective 1: To enhance capacities of Government teacher trainers and programme personnel on Inclusive Education
Objective 2: To demonstrate effective and functional Inclusive Education approach in selected schools
Objective 3: To advocate for the realisation of the Right to Education for disabled children, particularly VI/blind children
Objective 4: To develop and strengthen systems for inclusive education to take the project to scale</narrative>
  </description>
